    "title": "Modified NIH Stroke Scale/Score (mNIHSS)",
    "desc": "The Modified NIH Stroke Scale/Score (mNIHSS) calculates the shortened, validated version of NIH Stroke Scale for quantifying stroke severity.",
    "data": {
        "orgreference": [
            {
                "href": "https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/11387492",
                "text": "Lyden PD, Lu M, Levine SR, Brott TG, Broderick J; NINDS rtPA Stroke Study Group. A modified National Institutes of Health Stroke Scale for use in stroke clinical trials: preliminary reliability and validity. Stroke. 2001 Jun;32(6):1310-7."
